as Cl\u00e1sico' This Weekend |url=https://watchmendailyjournal.com/2019/08/03/another-visayas-clasico-weekend/ |accessdate=March 18, 2020 |publisher=Watchmen Daily Journal |date=August 3, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200318174738/https://watchmendailyjournal.com/2019/08/03/another-visayas-clasico-weekend/ |archivedate=March 18, 2020 |location=Bacolod}}</ref>\n|-\n| August 15, 2019 || MF || {{Flagicon|PHI}} || [[James Younghusband]] || 32 || Unattached || Free transfer || <ref>{{cite news |last1=Go |first1=Beatrice |title=James Younghusband joins Ceres in PFL return |url=https://www.rappler.com/sports/by-sport/football/237919-james-younghusband-philippine-league-return-ceres-negros-fc |accessdate=March 18, 2020 |agency=Rappler |date=August 17, 2019 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190819060645/https://www.rappler.com/sports/by-sport/football/237919-james-younghusband-philippine-league-return-ceres-negros-fc |archivedate=August 19, 2019}}</ref>\n|}\n\n=== Out ===\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"  style=\"text-align:center; font-size:90%; \"\n! style=\"background:#F8F500; color:#000000; width:150px;\"| Date\n! style=\"background:#F8F500; color:#000000; width:50px;\"| {{Tooltip|Pos.|Position}}\n! style=\"background:#F8F500; color:#000000; width:50px;\"| {{Tooltip|Nat.| Nationality}}\n! style=\"background:#F8F500; color:#000000; width:150px;\"| Name\n! style=\"background:#F8F500; color:#000000; width:30px;\"|{{Tooltip|Age|Age on the day of transfer}}\n! style=\"background:#F8F500; color:#000000; width:200px;\"| To\n! style=\"background:#F8F500; color:#000000; width:125px;\"| {{Tooltip|Type|Type of transfer}}\n! style=\"background:#F8F500; color:#000000; width:25px;\"| Ref.\n|-\n! colspan=8 | Pre-season\n|-\n| January 23, 2019 || [[Midfielder|MF]] || {{Flagicon|PHI}} || [[Manuel Ott]] || 26 || {{Flagicon|THA}} [[Ratchaburi Mitr Phol F.C.|Ratchaburi Mitr Phol]] || Free transfer || <ref name=\"Reich_Ott_exit\" /><ref>{{cite news |last1=Sharma |first1=Sa