 Football Association|Japan]])\n|result=W}}\n{{football box collapsible\n|id=\n|date={{Start date|2019|4|3|}}\n|time={{UTZ|19:30|8}}\n|round=Matchday 3\n|score=1\u20130\n|report=[http://www.the-afc.com/competitions/afc-cup/matches/2019/1034133 Live Report]<br />[http://stats.the-afc.com/match_report/14695 Stats Report]\n|team1=Ceres\u2013Negros {{flagicon|PHI}}\n|goals1=[[Bienvenido Mara\u00f1\u00f3n|Mara\u00f1\u00f3n]] {{goal|9}}\n|team2={{flagicon|IDN}} [[Persija Jakarta]]\n|goals2=\n|stadium=[[Panaad Park and Stadium]]\n|location=[[Bacolod]]\n|attendance=5,878\n|referee=[[Vahid Kazemi]] ([[Football Federation Islamic Republic of Iran|Iran]])\n|result=W}}\n{{football box collapsible\n|id=\n|date={{Start date|2019|4|23|}}\n{{refn|group=\"note\"|name=\"Persija Jakarta v Ceres\u2013Negros\"|The Persija Jakarta v Ceres\u2013Negros match was rescheduled from the original date of 16 April to 23 April due to its proximity to the [[2019 Indonesian general election|general election held in Indonesia the next day]].}}\n|time={{UTZ|16:00|6:30}}\n|round=Matchday 4\n|score=2\u20133\n|report=[http://www.the-afc.com/competitions/afc-cup/matches/2019/1034144 Live Report]<br />[http://stats.the-afc.com/match_report/14697 Stats Report]\n|team1=[[Persija Jakarta]] {{flagicon|IDN}}\n|goals1=\n*[[Sandi Darma Sute|Sandi]] {{goal|49}}\n*[[Bruno Oliveira de Matos|Matos]] {{goal|57}}\n|team2={{flagicon|PHI}} Ceres\u2013Negros\n|goals2=\n*[[Miguel Tanton|Tanton]] {{goal|70}}\n*[[Bienve Mara\u00f1\u00f3n|Mara\u00f1\u00f3n]] {{goal|85}}\n*[[Mike Ott|Ott]] {{goal|90+2}}\n|stadium=[[Gelora Bung Karno Stadium]]\n|location=[[Jakarta]]\n|attendance=26,923\n|referee=[[Sherzod Kasimov]] ([[Uzbekistan Football Association|Uzbekistan]])\n|result=W}}\n{{football box collapsible\n|id=\n|date={{Start date|2019|5|1|}}\n|time={{UTZ|15:30|6:30}}\n|round=Matchday 5\n|score=0\u20135\n|report=[http://www.the-afc.com/competitions/afc-cup/matches/2019/1034170 Live Report]<br />[http://stats.the-afc.com/match_re